== 争议 ==
=== 国际残奥委会主席开幕式、闭幕式致辞 ===
3月4日进行的开幕式期间，国际残奥委会主席[[安德鲁·帕森斯|安德鲁·帕森斯]]在讲话开头将“People's Republic”（人民共和国）口误为“Republic”（民国），但后来没有更正错误，接着说“China”（中国）；开幕次日，国际残奥委会就这一口误致歉，表示帕森斯因过于激动而酿成失误。<ref>{{Cite web|title=致歉声明|url=https://weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show?id=2309404743642261881036|access-date=2022-03-06|author=国际残疾人奥林匹克委员会|date=2022-03-05|publisher=[[新浪微博|新浪微博]]|language=zh-cn|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220309152703/https://weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show?id=2309404743642261881036|archivedate=2022-03-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=IPC apologises after Parsons mistakenly refers to Xi as "President of the Republic of China"|url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1120087/ipc-apologise-republic-of-china|accessdate=2022-03-06|date=2022-03-05|work=Inside the Games|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220305132259/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1120087/ipc-apologise-republic-of-china|archivedate=2022-03-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>

另外，因[[2022年俄羅斯入侵烏克蘭|2月24日俄罗斯出兵乌克兰]]，致辞时打破数十年来鲜少对政局表态的传统，表示：「在国际奥委会，我们渴望一个更美好、更包容，没有歧视，免于仇恨，免于无知，免于冲突的世界」，并补充道「奥林匹克休战是第76届联合国大会上193个会员国一致通过的联合国决议。它必须得到尊重和遵守，而不是违反。」<ref name=":122">{{Cite news|title=China Censors Paralympics Opening Ceremony, Premier League Over Ukraine|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/china-paralympics-opening-ceremony-premier-league-ukraine-11646410117|newspaper=Wall Street Journal|date=2022-03-04|accessdate=2022-03-05|issn=0099-9660|language=en-US|first=Jonathan Cheng and Joshua|last=Robinson|archivedate=2022-03-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220305132300/https://www.wsj.com/articles/china-paralympics-opening-ceremony-premier-league-ukraine-11646410117|dead-url=no}}</ref>相关内容在[[中央广播电视总台|中央广播电视总台]]转播中被忽略翻译，转播时帕森斯的声音音量也被调小，手語也暫停翻譯。<ref>{{cite news|author1=喬納森·郑（Jonathan Cheng)|author2=約書亞·羅賓遜(Joshua Robinson)|title=中国"审查"残奥会开幕式，超级联赛对乌克兰 (China Censors Paralympics Opening Ceremony, Premier League Over Ukraine)|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/china-paralympics-opening-ceremony-premier-league-ukraine-11646410117|accessdate=2022-03-05|work=华尔街日报(Wall Street Journal)|date=2022-03-04|archivedate=2022-03-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220305132259/https://www.wsj.com/articles/china-paralympics-opening-ceremony-premier-league-ukraine-11646410117|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=反战挺乌都不行：残奥会致辞被审查 德甲英超赛遭禁播|url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E5%8F%8D%E6%88%98%E6%8C%BA%E4%B9%8C%E9%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E8%A1%8C%E6%AE%8B%E5%A5%A5%E4%BC%9A%E8%87%B4%E8%BE%9E%E8%A2%AB%E5%AE%A1%E6%9F%A5-%E5%BE%B7%E7%94%B2%E8%8B%B1%E8%B6%85%E8%B5%9B%E9%81%AD%E7%A6%81%E6%92%AD/a-61027552|access-date=2022-03-06|date=2022-03-05|work=DW|language=zh-CN|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220306031657/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E5%8F%8D%E6%88%98%E6%8C%BA%E4%B9%8C%E9%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E8%A1%8C%E6%AE%8B%E5%A5%A5%E4%BC%9A%E8%87%B4%E8%BE%9E%E8%A2%AB%E5%AE%A1%E6%9F%A5-%E5%BE%B7%E7%94%B2%E8%8B%B1%E8%B6%85%E8%B5%9B%E9%81%AD%E7%A6%81%E6%92%AD/a-61027552|archivedate=2022-03-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>之后[[新华社|新华社]]发布的中文版演讲稿中也没有收录帕森斯反战相关致辞<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://ie.bjd.com.cn/5b165687a010550e5ddc0e6a/contentApp/61dbd0c1e4b0034fd88d67e8/AP62232565e4b02e911726a0db.html?isshare=1&contentType=0&isBjh=0|author=新华社|work=北京日报|date=2022-03-05|accessdate=2022-03-06|title=帕森斯在开幕式上的致辞|archivedate=2022-03-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220305183117/https://ie.bjd.com.cn/5b165687a010550e5ddc0e6a/contentApp/61dbd0c1e4b0034fd88d67e8/AP62232565e4b02e911726a0db.html?isshare=1&contentType=0&isBjh=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。国际残奥委会当晚就[[中国中央电视台|中国中央电视台]]忽略柏臣斯的发言一事，要求对方作出解释<ref>{{Cite web|title=Paralympic Body Asks China Why it Censored Anti-War Speech|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2022-03-05/paralympic-body-presses-china-on-censoring-of-no-war-speech|access-date=2022-03-05|work=www.bloomberg.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220305105152/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2022-03-05/paralympic-body-presses-china-on-censoring-of-no-war-speech|archivedate=2022-03-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隔日，国际残奥会发言人克雷格斯宾塞告诉[[法新社|法新社]]，他们已经等待了超过24小时，但仍然没有得到中国中央电视台的任何答复<ref>{{Cite web|title=War in Ukraine: the international committee accuses Beijing of censorship|url=https://www.world-today-news.com/war-in-ukraine-the-international-committee-accuses-beijing-of-censorship/|access-date=2022-03-07|date=2022-03-06|work=World Today News|language=en-US|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220307075419/https://www.world-today-news.com/war-in-ukraine-the-international-committee-accuses-beijing-of-censorship/|archivedate=2022-03-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。3月12日，国际残奥会再次重申，他们曾在3月5日向中国中央电视台寻求解释，但至今沒有得到任何回应<ref>{{Cite web|title=IPC still awaiting update from CCTV over Parsons speech translation controversy|url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1120447/ipc-awaiting-cctv-update|access-date=2022-03-14|date=1647081354|work=www.insidethegames.biz|archive-date=2022-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220405094341/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1120447/ipc-awaiting-cctv-update}}</ref>。

在[[2022年冬季残疾人奥林匹克运动会闭幕式|闭幕式]]上，帕森斯开始讲话时用重音强调了“People's”。{{Citation needed|time=2022-03-15T03:37:07+00:00}}另外据报道，中央广播电视总台的转播再次对致辞中宣扬和平的诉求作出调整，帕森斯提到“残奥村里有不同的民族，不同的观点，不同的能力， 这样的分歧并没有分裂我们，而是团结了我们携手共创未来。通过这种团结，我们有希望，包容的希望，和谐的希望，最重要的是和平的希望。”，最后一句“和平的希望”，转播翻译时改为“成为一个大家族的希望”；另外，帕森斯赞许选手是“希望的灯塔、和平的卫士”等词句中，转播时未将“和平的卫士”翻成中文。<ref>{{Cite web|title=北京冬残奥闭幕："和平"再遭审查 乌克兰选手返乡难|url=https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/junshiwaijiao/cm-03142022132500.html|access-date=2022-03-15|work=Radio Free Asia|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220404035044/https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/junshiwaijiao/cm-03142022132500.html}}</ref>

